                  </persName>
               
             was indicted for <rs id="t18121202-36-off204" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18121202-36-off204" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18121202-36-off204" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18121202-36-cd205" type="crimeDate">7th of November</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18121202-36-off204 t18121202-36-cd205"></join>, two coach-window glasses, value 5 l. and two other glasses, value 5 l. and a horse-cloth, value 10 s. the property of 
                     <persName id="t18121202-36-victim394" type="victimName">
                        John 
                        Knight
                     <interp inst="t18121202-36-victim394" type="surname" value="Knight"></interp>
