                        <interp inst="t18121202-36-victim394" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     </persName>
                  , privately in his coach-house
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>SECOND COUNT - the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18121202-36-victim396" type="victimName">
                     William 
                     Jay
                  <interp inst="t18121202-36-victim396" type="surname" value="Jay"></interp>
