            , privately in his coach-house.</p>
               <p>AND ANOTHER COUNT - stating it to be the property of 
               <persName id="t18121202-36-victim397" type="victimName">
                  James 
                  Conatty
               <interp inst="t18121202-36-victim397" type="surname" value="Conatty"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18121202-36-victim397" type="given" value="James"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18121202-36-victim397" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , 
               
                  <persName id="t18121202-36-victim399" type="victimName">
                     Thomas 
